  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "构造 +1/-1 前缀和",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "合法序列的充要条件：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "1. 任意位置的前缀和 $\\ge 0$；",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "2. 最终总和 $= 0$。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "一对匹配的括号<code>()</code>进行合法翻转（<code>()</code>变成<code>)(</code>）需要满足的条件：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "设 $s[i] = (, s[j] = ), i < j$，需满足 $min(pre[i],...,pre[j - 1]) \\ge 2$。",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "最长合法括号子序列",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "括号子序列（不要求连续）的最长合法长度结论：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$M = \\min_{0 \\le p \\le n} \\big( \\text{前缀}[1..p] \\text{中 \\texttt{(} 的个数} + \\text{后缀}[p+1..n] \\text{中 \\texttt{)} 的个数} \\big)$$\n答案为 $2M$。\n### 证明\n### 例子",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "树形结构",
      "level": 2,
